{"tid":884590,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來已經同你散左三個月了....","createTime":"2018-10-31T17:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T00:21:30.000Z","uid":95803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4b932cb4072a28154682f964e22cab8eb41c2e0d","tid":884590,"uid":95803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"我聽緊eason首黑暗中漫舞會諗起你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我經過火車站會諗起你返香港個陣<br />\n呃我話叫左朋友俾啲野 <br />\n但原來你係特登俾驚喜我早左一日返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見到三眼仔音樂盒會諗起你送俾我做聖誕禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓之前就會諗到我早排過澳洲搵你個21日<br />\n晚晚你都係我隔離攬住我訓 好開心<br />\n個陣我真係好想以後都留係到陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係點解你要屈我騷擾個女仔？<br />\n點解要用埋呢啲垃圾藉口飛我？<br />\n唔再中意我頂我唔順可以直接講 點解要屈我？<br />\n<br />\n當我真係接受左你已經離開我個陣<br />\n點解你要再搵返我講對唔住？<br />\n講對唔住有乜野用？<br />\n個刻清白你都還唔返俾我啦<br />\n個死貓我都食左啦 仲想點呀？<br />\n仲要話你分手你都唔想 係屋企人意思？<br />\n仲要搬幾多廢話出黎？<br />\n你話你好愛我 一直最愛個個都係我<br />\n係囉 個刻好愛 下一刻已經唔再愛呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就算鬧左你幾多次都好<br />\n我個心都仍然好憎你 憎你點解要屈我<br />\n同埋你啲朋友唔好屈得就屈<br />\n良心過唔過意得去 做人唔好咁賤格<br />\n我根本無做過呀 我發誓 我有做過我爛子宮呀dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你幾時到底會有報應 幾時先會十倍奉還係你身上？<br />\n<br />\n哈 點解我要喊 點解我仲要為你呢個垃圾廢柴喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7ad03e53ffccda7935e609be130cdef20a50c1","tid":884590,"uid":104017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T17:14:22.000Z","msg":"放過別人<br />\n放過自己<br />\n好好放低啦"},{"pid":"8ee1d982489fa7a10a31ec1098701ef783065b6f","tid":884590,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T17:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955b6a734dd9de69e2d4fcc7b0eea8579e998ac4","tid":884590,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T17:15:34.000Z","msg":"只係睇左第一句 我都好鐘意呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac3a7d70cee9d7369710170730117fcdd5f7228","tid":884590,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T17:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b07972de4a672c5446f1bac1050cd4338284320","tid":884590,"uid":95803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:21:30.000Z","msg":"訓醒 咪又係要返工 屌<br />\n放低自己個心會好過啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}